lead_paragraph: LEVINE--Carolyn M.,of Roslyn, New York on January 30, 2016. Beloved wife of the late Lee R. Levine. Mother of Ira (Betsy) and Bill (Carol). Grandmother of Rose and Ruby. 1/3
